snippet.title: Half-Life 2: RESISTANCE ELEMENT - Full Walkthrough
snippet.description:

Available via Steam this a fun romp that's a bit different than the usual Half-Life 2 Mods. Loved the space battle! Laughed so much I wet myself :)
